reviewText:
Well, I own #835 of 1200 bought new for apx $15.00 US, but I found mine by looking EVERYWHERE on the internet before running across it even at any new price under $90.00 US.

This film will creep you OUT!!! Just so gritty and dirty, it will leave you feeling that you have defied the Hand of God and need a bath!!! Not a film for the morally bankrupt.
